OL,3,CTeenage boy denies attempted murder of
OL,4,Cteacher at Milford Haven School
OL,6,FA teenage boy has denied the attempted
OL,7,Fmurder of a teacher at a school in
OL,8,FPembrokeshire.
OL,10,FThe boy, who cannot be named for legal
OL,11,Freasons, was charged with attempted
OL,12,Fmurder as well as causing grievous
OL,13,Fbodily harm (GBH) with intent, and
OL,14,Funlawful wounding, using a knife.
OL,16,FOn Friday (8 May), the teenager
OL,17,Fappeared at Swansea Crown Court and
OL,18,Fpleaded not guilty to those charges.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/3
