OL,3,CTeenage boy denies attempted murder of
OL,4,Cteacher at Milford Haven School
OL,6,FMilford Haven School was locked down
OL,7,Fat around 3:20pm on February 5
OL,8,Ffollowing reports a teacher had been
OL,9,Fassaulted by a pupil "brandishing a
OL,10,Fweapon".
OL,12,FThe teacher was discharged from
OL,13,Fhospital within hours of the incident
OL,14,Fand all pupils were "unharmed",
OL,15,Faccording to police statements from
OL,16,Fthe time.
OL,18,FThe boy has been remanded in custody
OL,19,Fahead of a trial scheduled for 6 July.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/3
